Description: OPPS-COMMENTS
        =============
        
        Install
        -------
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            pip install -e git+https://github.com/opps/opps-comments.git#egg=opps-comments
        
        
        
        Configuration
        -------------
        
        Include `opps.comments` on your django settings:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            INSTALLED_APPS += (
                'opps.comments',
            )
        
        
        Add Opps Comments credentials on your django settings:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            OPPS_COMMENTS = {
                "disqus": {
                    "shortname": "opps",
                },
                "facebook": {
                    "APP_ID": "123456"
                },
                "google": {}
            }
        
        
        
        Used
        ----
        
        .. code-block:: html
        
            {% load comments_tags %}
            {% load_comments %}
        
